  "tile_size_reference": 64,
  "summary": "Local-only HoMM3 terrain renderer prototype. Terrain and road frames are staged from extracted HoMM3 DEF assets for renderer study only, not for shippable/distributable art. Current logical terrain ids and map/editor/save/pathing data remain unchanged; rendering resolves land transitions through dirt or sand bridge/base families, water through shoreline-specific lookup, and roads through 4-neighbor overlay masks.",
